Function Reference/is subdomain install « WordPress Codex
-----------

Whether a sub-domain configuration is enabled. This function was added
in version 3.0.0.

Usage
-----

` <?php is_subdomain_install(); ?> `

Parameters
----------

None

Return Values
-------------

 (Boolean) 
:   True if sub-domain configuration is enabled, false otherwise.

Source File
-----------

`is_subdomain_install()` is located in `wp-includes/ms-load.php`.

See also
--------

See also index of [Function
Reference](/Function_Reference "Function Reference") and index of
[Template Tags](/Template_Tags "Template Tags").

